---
// HowItWorks.astro — Three-step section
---

<section class="how-section" id="how">
  <div class="how-inner">
    <div class="how-header" data-reveal>
      <span class="section-eyebrow">How it works</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Three steps to observability</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Integrate in minutes. No agent framework lock-in. Works with LangChain, CrewAI, AutoGen, or your own stack.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="how-steps">
      <div class="how-step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <div class="how-step-number">01</div>
        <h3>Install the SDK</h3>
        <p>Add the Kitaru SDK to your project. A single <code>pip install kitaru</code> and two lines of config.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        <div class="how-step-number">02</div>
        <h3>Run your agents</h3>
        <p>Kitaru instruments LLM calls, tool invocations, and gate checks automatically — zero code changes to your agent logic.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <div class="how-step-number">03</div>
        <h3>Observe and optimize</h3>
        <p>Open the dashboard to trace runs, compare versions, find prompt regressions, and cut costs — all in real time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-section {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }
  .how-inner {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 120px 48px;
  }
  .how-header { margin-bottom: 72px; }

  .how-steps {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 48px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .how-steps::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 28px; left: calc(16.66% + 28px); right: calc(16.66% + 28px);
    height: 1px; background: var(--color-border);
  }
  .how-step { position: relative; }
  .how-step-number {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
  }
  .how-step h3 {
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .how-step p {
    font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  .how-step code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px;
    background: var(--color-bg); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .how-inner { padding: 80px 20px; }
  }
</style>
